  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the town of Willoughby</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PREPARE YOUR DEFENSES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an assortment of items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the effects of items to your liking via the mutator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the optimal item loadout and placement depending on the level</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EXTERMINATE YOUR ENEMIES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine effects using items, weapons, or doll ability to deal damage to enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killing enemies grants eggs which are used to purchase various things outside of levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect doll parts to gain terminal points faster</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PURCHASE UPGRADES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/9d51a71555b933920a17a6c49cd4353b.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/9d51a71555b933920a17a6c49cd4353b.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/9d51a71555b933920a17a6c49cd4353b.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade damage, item speed, or restock inventory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase boons to change how effects and other aspects of gameplay function</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make decisions that will have a significant impact on your run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CREATE YOUR PERFECT DOLL</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/794496cad27b0973385caea894691569.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/794496cad27b0973385caea894691569.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/794496cad27b0973385caea894691569.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mold your little guy into their true form</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different parts provide different in level benefits, like perks and abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose yourself in the beauty of creation</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the town of Willoughby</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PREPARE YOUR DEFENSES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/a5a919b50b1ba48dd2c8dd98c2b82945.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an assortment of items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change the effects of items to your liking via the mutator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the optimal item loadout and placement depending on the level</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EXTERMINATE YOUR ENEMIES</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.poster.avif?t=1772000505\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.webm?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3590840/extras/38a0617f917d6c106c23a7359f20491d.mp4?t=1772000505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine effects using